(2)parse attributes to a weighted integer array.(?)
(3)stench is safer than breezy, beacuse there is one wumpus, but multiple pits
(4)if Breeze, then mark the adjacent slots as "Possible Pit"
(5)if Stench, then mark the adjacent slots as "Possible Wumpus"
(6)if Empty, then remove the adjacent slots as "Possible Pit" and "Possible Wumpus"
(7)if Glitter, then grab gold and trace back the safe path to the start.
(8)Have a array to store the shortest safest path from the start to the current slot.

